Package: rm501
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mitsubishi RM-501 Movemaster II robot simulator
 An app that simulates the Mitsubishi RM-501 Movemaster II robot.
   * SDL2 OpenGL GUI, Curses GUI,
   * control from computer keyboard, Gamepad or 3D mouse,
   * forward and inverse kinematics (double precision math),
   * implemented in one C file for simplicity and portability.

